{"type":"message","id":"552e5598","parentId":"29aca4dd","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:48:37.310Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to create the HOOK.md and handler.js files for this hook. Let me look at the session-memory handler more carefully to understand what I can access.\n\nThe key thing I need from the `command:new` event is:\n- `context.previousSessionEntry` - the previous session's data\n- `context.sessionEntry` - current session entry (might be the new one or about to be reset)\n- `context.sessionFile` - transcript file path\n- `context.workspaceDir` - workspace directory\n\nThe handler needs to:\n1. Get the previous session's transcript (using the approach from session-memory)\n2. Write it to `memory/LAST_SESSION.md` with the sessionId and a marker\n\n\n3. The new session startup will then read this file and know to inject it\n\nNow I'm writing the handler file.","thinkingSignature":"c6610a886f413e4804cd353c7c7911e29fd5ad9ff62723d21cde4b58e9060ca2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ul5opg048jzm_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\hooks\\last-session\\HOOK.md","content":"---\nname: last-session\ndescription: \"Saves the previous session's transcript to LAST_SESSION.md when /new is issued, enabling zero-beat context resume\"\nhomepage: https://docs.openclaw.ai/automation/hooks#last-session\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"emoji\": \"🔄\",\n      \"events\": [\"command:new\"],\n      \"requires\": { \"config\": [\"workspace.dir\"] }\n    }\n  }\n---\n\n# Last Session Hook\n\nWhen `/new` is issued, saves the previous session's full transcript to `memory/LAST_SESSION.md` so the next session can resume without missing a beat.\n\n## What It Does\n\n1. Fires on `command:new`\n2. Locates the previous session's transcript (via `context.previousSessionEntry` or fallback search)\n3. Extracts all user/assistant messages\n4. Writes them to `memory/LAST_SESSION.md` with session metadata header\n5. The session startup sequence reads this file and injects its contents\n\n## Output Format\n\n```markdown\n# LAST SESSION (Session ID: abc123)\n**DO NOT clear or delete this file until the new session has started.**\n\n## Previous Session Context\n\n[full transcript of previous conversation]\n\n---\n```\n\nThe startup sequence reads this file and injects the transcript into the new session's context.\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35902,"output":501,"cacheRead":12650,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49053,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774226904339}}
