{"type":"message","id":"ae3c7e19","parentId":"13147c8e","timestamp":"2026-03-23T01:14:45.821Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach is greeting me back. I just restarted the gateway and set up the last-session hook. Let me greet him back naturally.","thinkingSignature":"41ff0fb0b404c57e74a2e08e4a873f5e5ae5a55cedc5d8be29698bb00cf17d42"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! ✨ Yeah, just did a quick setup — installed a hook so when you hit `/new`, I grab the previous session's transcript and inject it into the next one. Should be seamless now.\n\nWhat do you need?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":78,"cacheRead":4246,"cacheWrite":41865,"totalTokens":46232,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774228480005}}
