{"type":"message","id":"c97a9e73","parentId":"502367d4","timestamp":"2026-03-23T01:34:26.382Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me fix the generate_text function to properly handle the requests patching. The issue is `original_post` isn't defined in the outer scope. Let me rewrite this more cleanly using a context manager approach.","thinkingSignature":"4091b58c6a48cdb346c0b402d6f2b84301f89d502b80c647ea6f52df89e947a5"},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me fix the `generate_text` function with a cleaner approach to patching requests:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xmegbocode5h_1","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":200,"limit":80,"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\\spark\\demo.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":63450,"output":121,"cacheRead":12730,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76301,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774229661178}}
{"type":"message","id":"f470b1d6","parentId":"c97a9e73","timestamp":"2026-03-23T01:34:26.394Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_xmegbocode5h_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    top_concepts: list,\n    theme: str,\n    mode: str = \"creative\",\n    ollama_url: str = None,\n    model: str = \"qwen2.5:7b\",\n    seed_moment: str = None,\n    user_constraints: list = None,\n) -> str:\n    \"\"\"\n    Map top concepts to creative text using CreativeMapper.\n    Falls back to a poetic concept description if no LLM available.\n    \n    Args:\n        top_concepts: Ordered list of concept names (first = highest activation)\n        theme: The driving theme\n        mode: creative | divergent | exploratory\n        ollama_url: Ollama API URL (if None, uses OpenAI/Anthropic env vars)\n        model: Model name for Ollama\n        seed_moment: A specific moment/detail/seed text to anchor the piece\n        user_constraints: List of elements the user wants in the piece\n    \"\"\"\n    # Import CreativeMapper lazily\n    try:\n        from spark.core.llm_mapper import CreativeMapper, find_tensions_in_concepts, sample_drift_path\n    except ImportError:\n        return \"[ERROR: Could not import CreativeMapper. Run from spark/ directory or check PYTHONPATH.]\"\n\n    # Build activation dict from ordered concept list\n    # Earlier in list = higher activation\n    concept_activations = {}\n    for i, concept in enumerate(top_concepts):\n        # Decay activation based on position\n        activation = max(0.05, 0.95 - (i * 0.05))\n        concept_activations[concept] = activation\n\n    # Determine provider\n    if ollama_url:\n        provider = \"ollama\"\n    elif os.environ.get(\"OPENAI_API_KEY\"):\n        provider = \"openai\"\n    elif os.environ.get(\"ANTHROPIC_API_KEY\"):\n        provider = \"anthropic\"\n    else:\n        provider = \"ollama\"  # Default to Ollama if available locally\n\n    mapper = CreativeMapper(provider=provider, model=model)\n    \n    # Override Ollama URL if specified (CreativeMapper uses localhost:11434 by default)\n    if ollama_url and provider == \"ollama\":\n        # Patch the URL into the mapper's client temporarily\n        import requests\n        original_post = requests.post\n        \n        def patched_post(url, json, timeout):\n            return original_post(f\"{ollama_url}/api/generate\", json=json, timeout=timeout)\n        \n        import types\n        requests.post = patched_post\n\n    try:\n        results = mapper.map_concepts_to_text(\n            concept_activations=concept_activations,\n            theme=theme,\n            mode=mode,\n            n_variations=1,\n            seed_moment=seed_moment,\n            user_constraints=user_constraints,\n        )\n        return results[0][\"text\"] if results else \"[No output]\"\n    except Exception as e:\n        return f\"[Generation error: {e}]\"\n    finally:\n        if ollama_url and provider == \"ollama\":\n            requests.post = original_post\n\n\n# -------------------------------------------------------------------\n# INTERACTIVE MODE\n# -------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n\n[138 more lines in file. Use offset=280 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774229666389}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ca219b5","parentId":"f470b1d6","timestamp":"2026-03-23T01:34:34.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The code looks fine actually — `original_post` is assigned before the `try` block so it's in scope in the `finally` block. But let me rewrite this to be cleaner using a proper approach. The `requests.post` patching is a bit hacky. Let me just set theOLLAMA URL differently.\n\nActually, looking at the CreativeMapper's `_generate` method, it hardcodes `http://localhost:11434`. So I need to either:\n1. Patch requests.post (what I was doing)\n2. Set an environment variable\n3. Modify CreativeMapper to accept a base URL\n\nThe cleanest solution for now is to patch requests.post within a context manager. \n\nI realize `original_post` is actually already defined before the try block, so my approach should work — let me verify by testing it rather than overthinking this further.","thinkingSignature":"eb7b12c1655f1404c1890299debfc76b591b937c31e79df7c16cf538c92cd3dd"},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me update the interactive function to ask for seed moment, and update the CLI args:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_amhrfxkh2b4g_1","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":280,"limit":60,"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\\spark\\demo.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":64252,"output":255,"cacheRead":12730,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77237,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774229666396}}
{"type":"message","id":"1dcf0a12","parentId":"2ca219b5","timestamp":"2026-03-23T01:34:34.064Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_amhrfxkh2b4g_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def print_banner():\n    print()\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n    print(\"  SPARK — Interactive Creative Writing Demo\")\n    print(\"  Drift Chamber + Thematic Graph + LLM\")\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n    print()\n\n\ndef print_domains():\n    print(\"Available domains:\")\n    for domain in [\"all\", \"romance\", \"scifi\", \"thriller\", \"literary\", \"horror\", \"poetry\"]:\n        desc = {\n            \"all\": \"All creative concepts\",\n            \"romance\": \"Love, longing, connection, loss\",\n            \"scifi\": \"Technology, cosmos, humanity, creation\",\n            \"thriller\": \"Tension, power, pursuit, secrets\",\n            \"literary\": \"Craft, meaning, form, expression\",\n            \"horror\": \"Death, dread, flesh, threshold\",\n            \"poetry\": \"Sensory, image, rhythm, metaphor\",\n        }[domain]\n        print(f\"  {domain:12s} — {desc}\")\n    print()\n\n\ndef print_modes():\n    print(\"Modes:\")\n    for mode in [\"creative\", \"divergent\", \"exploratory\"]:\n        desc = {\n            \"creative\": \"Balanced: coherent + exploratory\",\n            \"divergent\": \"Maximum surprise, subverts expectations\",\n            \"exploratory\": \"Contemplative, carefully observed\",\n        }[mode]\n        print(f\"  {mode:12s} — {desc}\")\n    print()\n\n\ndef interactive():\n    print_banner()\n    print_domains()\n    print_modes()\n\n    # Get user choices\n    domain = input(\"Domain [all]: \").strip().lower() or \"all\"\n    theme = input(\"Theme [love in the age of AI]: \").strip() or \"love in the age of AI\"\n    steering = float(input(\"Steering strength [0.3]: \").strip() or \"0.3\")\n    mode = input(\"Mode [creative]: \").strip().lower() or \"creative\"\n    n_outputs = int(input(\"Number of outputs [2]: \").strip() or \"2\")\n    ollama_url = input(\"Ollama URL (Enter to skip) [none]: \").strip() or None\n    if ollama_url and not ollama_url.startswith(\"http\"):\n        ollama_url = f\"http://{ollama_url}\"\n\n    print()\n    print(f\"Building {domain} concept graph...\")\n    graph, concept_to_cluster, goal_concepts, concepts = build_thematic_graph(domain)\n    print(f\"  {len(graph.nodes)} concepts, {sum(len(n.neighbors) for n in graph.nodes.values())//2} edges\")\n\n    print(f\"Running drift (steering={steering}, steps=30)...\")\n    graph, history = run_drift(graph, concept_to_cluster, goal_concepts, steering=steering)\n    print(f\"  Final: {len(graph.get_strong_nodes(0.3))} strong concepts\")\n\n[78 more lines in file. Use offset=340 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774229674054}}
