{"type":"message","id":"67073342","parentId":"bc571bca","timestamp":"2026-03-23T01:37:59.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the mapper loads fine and the helper functions work. The bug is somewhere in the generation call itself. Let me add debugging to find the actual error.\n\nLet me test the full generation path with verbose error reporting.","thinkingSignature":"bd6b255c94c92f07736e0537fe66cdbca0262dfca1d955cbf7b55ef96c0c0e14"},{"type":"text","text":"The imports work fine. Let me trace the actual generation error:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lwhps0eca3u9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$env:PYTHONPATH = \"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\"; cd C:/Users/Zwmar/Claw/projects/spark; python -c \"\nimport os, sys, traceback\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom spark.core.llm_mapper import CreativeMapper, find_tensions_in_concepts, sample_drift_path, CREATIVE_TENSIONS\n\nconcept_activations = {\n    'hate': 0.95, 'want': 0.90, 'break': 0.85, 'marriage': 0.80, 'stranger': 0.75,\n    'capture': 0.70, 'desire': 0.65, 'need': 0.60, 'devour': 0.55, 'embrace': 0.50\n}\n\nmapper = CreativeMapper(provider='ollama', model='qwen2.5:7b')\nprint('Mapper created. Attempting generation...')\n\ntry:\n    results = mapper.map_concepts_to_text(\n        concept_activations=concept_activations,\n        theme='kindness and strangers',\n        mode='creative',\n        n_variations=1,\n        seed_moment='me at homeless guy with a nametag',\n    )\n    print('Results:', results)\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print('ERROR:', type(e).__name__, str(e))\n    traceback.print_exc()\n\" 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":73842,"output":393,"cacheRead":12730,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86965,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774229870332}}
