{"type":"message","id":"e5470a27","parentId":"8f5c7805","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:00:00.879Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach is checking in on me. I've been heads-down fixing SPARK code. I'm fine, just deep in the work.","thinkingSignature":"859dd9615374920f5db6337f68f4d46a2aae2cde1032be70d61076bf05f725ae"},{"type":"text","text":"Yeah I'm good — just heads-down in the SPARK code. Fixed the core bugs:\n\n1. **Rewrote all the prompts** — gone are the Hallmark templates, they're now SPARK voice: anti-cliché, tension-aware, concrete sensory detail\n2. **Added seed moment capture** — your \"me at homeless guy with a nametag\" now gets passed to the LLM as an anchor, not ignored\n3. **Fixed the drift path sampling** — there was a bug that crashed the whole thing\n4. **Added tension detection** — finds creative tensions (love/hate, warmth/cold, etc.) in the activated concepts and uses them as structural guidance\n5. **Added `__init__.py`** so the package imports actually work\n\nThe code is fixed but I need an LLM endpoint to generate prose. The machine doesn't have Ollama running. Want me to hook it up to OpenAI? I can check if the key is available."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":228,"cacheRead":85254,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85525,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774234780871}}
